{"id":150,"date":"2015-07-01T10:28:04","date_gmt":"2015-07-01T04:58:04","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/ewokesoft.com\/blog\/?p=150"},"modified":"2015-07-01T10:28:04","modified_gmt":"2015-07-01T04:58:04","slug":"how-to-install-wordpress","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/how-to-install-wordpress\/","title":{"rendered":"How to Install WordPress?"},"content":{"rendered":"<h3 class=\"heading h3\"><span class=\"step\">STEP 1. <\/span>Download the WordPress installation package<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi7-614x240-1.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-199 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi7-614x240-1.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 614px) 100vw, 614px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi7-614x240-1.jpg 614w, http:\/\/ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi7-614x240-300x117.jpg 300w\" alt=\"wpi7-614x240\" width=\"614\" height=\"240\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>To start the installation process, first you need to download WordPress from it\u00e2\u20ac\u2122s O<a href=\"http:\/\/wordpress.org\/download\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">fficial Download Page<\/a>. We recommend that you always download and install the latest stable version of WordPress.<\/p>\n<p>Once you click on the <strong>Download<\/strong> button for the latest WordPress version, the installation package will be saved to your hard disk. Locate the installation package that you\u00e2\u20ac\u2122ve just downloaded and extract it to a new folder.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"heading h3\"><span class=\"step\">STEP 2. <\/span>Upload the WordPress Files to Your Server<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi8-470x240-1.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-208 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi8-470x240-1.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 470px) 100vw, 470px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi8-470x240-1.jpg 470w, http:\/\/ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi8-470x240-300x153.jpg 300w\" alt=\"wpi8-470x240\" width=\"470\" height=\"240\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Now, you need to upload the extracted files and folders to your web server. The easiest way to upload the installation files is via FTP. Once the download is complete, extract the archive and upload it to your web hosting account. You can do that via FTP using a client application like Filezilla or via cPanel -&gt; File Manager -&gt; Upload file(s). If you want this WordPress installation to be main for your website, the files should reside in the public_html folder of your account. However, you can always make a subfolder (i.e. public_html\/blog) if you want to run only part of your website on WordPress.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"heading h3\"><span class=\"step\">STEP 3. <\/span>Create a MySQL Database for WordPress to use<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi9-571x240-1.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-204\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi9-571x240-1.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 571px) 100vw, 571px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi9-571x240-1.jpg 571w, http:\/\/ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi9-571x240-300x126.jpg 300w\" alt=\"wpi9-571x240\" width=\"571\" height=\"240\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Now, you need to create a MySQL database and assign a user to it with full permissions. Once you create your MySQL Database and User, make sure you write down the database name, database username and password you\u00e2\u20ac\u2122ve just created. You will need those for the installation process.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"heading h3\"><span class=\"step\">STEP 4. <\/span>Go through the installation process<\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi1-607x240-1.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-207\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi1-607x240-1.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 607px) 100vw, 607px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi1-607x240-1.jpg 607w, http:\/\/ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi1-607x240-300x119.jpg 300w\" alt=\"wpi1-607x240\" width=\"607\" height=\"240\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Now it\u00e2\u20ac\u2122s time to navigate to your website to start with the installation process. If you have uploaded WordPress in your public_html directory you\u00e2\u20ac\u2122ll need to go to <strong>http:\/\/yourdomain.com<\/strong> in your preferred browser. The first thing you will notice is a message, telling you that you don\u00e2\u20ac\u2122t have a wp-config.php file and you should create one. Just click on the Create a Configuration File button to proceed.<\/p>\n<p>On this page you will see a message, asking you to prepare the necessary information for the installation. Since we already have this information, simply press the <strong>Go!<\/strong> button.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi2-349x240-1.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-203\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi2-349x240-1.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 349px) 100vw, 349px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi2-349x240-1.jpg 349w, http:\/\/ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi2-349x240-300x206.jpg 300w\" alt=\"wpi2-349x240\" width=\"349\" height=\"240\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Enter the details for your newly created MySQL database and press the <strong>Sumbit<\/strong> button<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi3-349x240-1.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-205 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi3-349x240-1.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 349px) 100vw, 349px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi3-349x240-1.jpg 349w, http:\/\/ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi3-349x240-300x206.jpg 300w\" alt=\"wpi3-349x240\" width=\"349\" height=\"240\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>WordPress will now check if your settings are correct. If you have entered all the necessary information, you will see a confirmation screen. Press the <strong>Run the Install<\/strong> button to proceed.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi4-630x213-1.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-200\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi4-630x213-1.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi4-630x213-1.jpg 630w, http:\/\/ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi4-630x213-300x101.jpg 300w\" alt=\"wpi4-630x213\" width=\"630\" height=\"213\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>On the next screen you will have to enter the information about your administrative username and the title of your new site. In addition, you can specify whether you\u00e2\u20ac\u2122d want search engines to index your site or not. Once you fill in that information, press the Install WordPress button. Bear in mind, however, that you should specify a real email address. It can be later used in case you forget your password.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi5-217x240-1.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-201 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi5-217x240-1.jpg\" alt=\"wpi5-217x240\" width=\"217\" height=\"240\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi6-456x240-1.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-202\" src=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi6-456x240-1.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 456px) 100vw, 456px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi6-456x240-1.jpg 456w, http:\/\/ewokesoft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/07\/wpi6-456x240-300x158.jpg 300w\" alt=\"wpi6-456x240\" width=\"456\" height=\"240\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>STEP 1. Download the WordPress installation package To start the installation process, first you need to download WordPress from it\u00e2\u20ac\u2122s Official Download Page. We recommend that you always download and install the latest stable version of WordPress. Once you click on the Download button for the latest WordPress version, the&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":206,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[3],"tags":[17],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v21.3 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>How to Install WordPress? - Magento, Ecommerce Development Company in Kochi, Kerala, India<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.ewokesoft.com\/how-to-install-wordpress\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"How to Install WordPress? - Magento, Ecommerce Development Company in Kochi, Kerala, India\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"STEP 1. Download the WordPress installation package To start the insta